platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Treasure-seeking pirates, time-travelling nurses and an old friend who slices up the undead with his chainsaw hand: theres a lot to love about STARZ. The app has a gorgeous layout stuffed with some of our favourite content, from recent Marvel films and Oscar-winning dramas to STARZ original series like Black Sails, Outlander and Ash vs. Evil Dead. With the ability to subscribe right from the app and download shows for offline viewing, its a shiny go-to in our entertainment galaxy.
